doc ///
  Key
    expectedBetti
    (expectedBetti,RingElement)
  Headline
    compute the expected betti table from the Hilbert numerator
  Usage
    B=expectedBetti q
  Inputs
    q: RingElement
       a polynomial in ZZ[t]
  Outputs
